label: Date
desc: The date when the game was played

label: Home Team
desc: The host team (number in brackets represents position of that team on the table at that moment)

label: Away Team
desc: The visitor team (number in brackets represents position of that team on the table at that moment)

label: Goals
desc: The number of goals scored by the player

label: Assists
desc: The number of assists made by the player

label: Own Goals
desc: The number of OWN goals scored by the player

label: Yellow Card
desc: Whether the player received a yellow card or not

label: 2nd Yellow
desc: Whether the player received a SECOND yellow card or not

label: Red Card
desc: Whether the player received a DIRECT red card or not

label: Min In
desc: Minute of the game when the player entered the field.

label: Min Out
desc: Minute of the game when the player was substituted and replaced by another player.

label: Competition
desc: Full name or abbreviation of the competition
